data.description: Seller will pay $5000.00 of Buyer's closing cost!! Large home located in Hickory Ridge Subdivision. This four-bedroom, four-bath home has everything. The remote owner's suite has an office/nursery and his and her bathrooms. Yes, you read that right ladies. A circular driveway brings you and your guests right to your double front doors. Upon entering to your right is the breakfast room that opens to the kitchen. The kitchen has been updated with granite countertops and a copper apron front sink. You step down into a sunken living room with soaring cathedral ceilings and a wood-burning brick fireplace. French doors lead to a huge back deck that spans the width of the house. There's also a wet bar, formal dining room, a bonus room/theater upstairs, and an oversized 2-car garage.
